                            oc:hasContent [ a oc:CodeExample ;
                                    oc:blockType "code_block" ;
                                    oc:codeContent """---
description: Deploy with shorthand
argument-hint: [env-shorthand]
---

Input: $1

Expanding shorthand:
- d/dev → development
- s/stg → staging
- p/prod → production

case "$1" in
  d|dev) ENV="development";;
  s|stg) ENV="staging";;
  p|prod) ENV="production";;
  *) ENV="$1";;
esac

Deploying to: $ENV
""" ;
